gation. Nevertheless, cosmology based on\n$k\\gtrsim 0.1h/$Mpc velocity data shall be careful this potential velocity\nbias.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Oct 2014 05:33:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Jun 2015 02:27:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
