at extend from\nthe reconnection plane, four angles $\\theta_i$ between these arms are found,\nthen summed, giving $\\sum\\theta_i>360^\\circ$. This implies that the overall\nstructure is convex or hyperbolic, as opposed to the acute angles of the\nanti-parallel pyramid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Oct 2014 05:42:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Feb 2016 19:28:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-18"}
